The paper discusses the development of a customisable portal component for monitoring resources, services, and computations in Grid computing. This falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the use of the Google Maps API to provide an interactive user interface, which could fall under Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses the management of heterogeneous and distributed sources, which could fall under Computer Engineering (cs.CE) and Software Engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the use of Grid computing for collaboration in large scale environments, which could fall under Distributed Systems (cs.Distributed Systems).
